      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically robust E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This powerplant features six individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system, delivering 333 hp with a visceral 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and an M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring precise torque distribution during spirited cornering. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including rear subframe reinforcement and a VANOS system overhaul, addressing the primary structural and mechanical concerns of the chassis. The suspension maintains its factory-designed kinematics with MacPherson struts and a multi-link rear, providing the communicative feedback and neutral handling balance expected of this M-division icon. A well-sorted driver's car with an emphasis on performance integrity.",
